Excited to be part of this new amazing game @journeytofoundation. I had a blast recording it and can’t wait to see the finished product!! “Well, according to my teachers, the only thing I’m good at is talking people into doing things they’ll later regret... so, I suppose it was inevitable.”

Ritesh Rajan, the voice of Ken in numerous Barbie spin-offs and Farran in Russian Doll, will be portraying Kaldan Morrow in Journey to Foundation.

@teshrajan’s friendly and playful voice acting is the perfect fit for Kaldan’s charismatic and easygoing personality, even while escaping from pirates across plasma storms (while also trying to find a place where he can belong).

#charactervoice #gameVO #voiceacting #voiceactor #castreveal #voiceover

Our next insanely talented and handsome judge @teshrajan !!
This guy is such a celebrity, even his baby pictures have the Getty Images watermark.  You can usually find Ritesh Rajan in the credits of perfect score tomato movies, but he’s even the official voice of Ken in every Barbie animation of which there are infinite.  Also, if you ever played a dance video game with a Bhangra category, you were probably copying him straight up, and now he’s out for revenge.  Everything he touches turns spicy, so taste your hand after you shake his.  It’s delicious.
